:"Spider-Man: Far From Home","original_language":"en"},{"id":671,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","video":false,"overview":"Harry Potter has lived under the stairs at his aunt and uncle's house his whole life. But on his 11th birthday, he learns he's a powerful wizard—with a place waiting for him at the Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. As he learns to harness his newfound powers with the help of the school's kindly headmaster, Harry uncovers the truth about his parents' deaths—and about the villain who's to blame.","genre_ids":[12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.5675,"vote_count":29171,"poster_path":"/wuMc08IPKEatf9rnMNXvIDxqP4W.jpg","release_date":"2001-11-16","vote_average":7.899,"backdrop_path":"/1XAC6RPT01UX9EQGy2JVn5c8pgy.jpg","original_title":"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":189,"adult":false,"title":"Sin City: A Dame to Kill For","video":false,"overview":"Some of Sin City's most hard-boiled citizens cross paths with a few of its more reviled inhabitants.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":5.0792,"vote_count":4078,"poster_path":"/50kALxDX4mmzIRljbNbPY0u4cie.jpg","release_date":"2014-08-20","vote_average":6.402,"backdrop_path":"/rxMnmklIpunsNsRkQ7hw61ZJa84.jpg","original_title":"Sin City: A Dame to Kill For","original_language":"en"},{"id":437,"adult":false,"title":"Cube 2: Hypercube","video":false,"overview":"Eight strangers awaken with no memory, in a puzzling cube-shaped room where the laws of physics do not always apply.","genre_ids":[53,878,9648],"popularity":2.2669,"vote_count":1565,"poster_path":"/bEqqwtwUP7lm56VyeVONhv9JtYu.jpg","release_date":"2002-04-15","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/zJqv6s4XCdHWrnoqfLqlGzzxSjH.jpg","original_title":"Cube 2: Hypercube","original_language":"en"},{"id":176,"adult":false,"title":"Saw","video":false,"overview":"Two men wake up to find themselves shackled in a grimy, abandoned bathroom. As they struggle to comprehend their predicament, they discover a disturbing tape left behind by the sadistic mastermind known as Jigsaw. With a chilling voice and cryptic instructions, Jigsaw informs them that they must partake in a gruesome game in order to secure their freedom.","genre_ids":[27,9648,80],"popularity":7.7394,"vote_count":9880,"poster_path":"/rLNSOudrayDBo1uqXjrhxcjODIC.jpg","release_date":"2004-10-01","vote_average":7.419,"backdrop_path":"/ok4ot3YbfDYZcINXf91JUfq3maB.jpg","original_title":"Saw","original_language":"en"},{"id":319,"adult":false,"title":"True Romance","video":false,"overview":"Clarence marries hooker Alabama, steals cocaine from her pimp, and tries to sell it in Hollywood, while the owners of the coke try to reclaim it.","genre_ids":[28,80,10749],"popularity":4.3693,"vote_count":2983,"poster_path":"/39lXk6ud6KiJgGbbWI2PUKS7y2.jpg","release_date":"1993-09-09","vote_average":7.535,"backdrop_path":"/1Uh8yuXlFcMDpVHWZJidjanT06e.jpg","original_title":"True Romance","original_language":"en"},{"id":332,"adult":false,"title":"Inspector Gadget","video":false,"overview":"John Brown is a bumbling but well-intentioned security guard who is badly injured in an explosion planned by an evil mastermind. He is taken to a laboratory, where Brenda, a leading robotics surgeon, replaces his damaged limbs with state-of-the-art gadgets and tools. Named \"Inspector Gadget\" by the press, John -- along with his niece, Penny, and her trusty dog, Brain -- uses his new powers to discover who was behind the explosion.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,10751],"popularity":1.9193,"vote_count":1292,"poster_path":"/dDcsv1Lql5aM6H4JYfDHjBAXKgT.jpg","release_date":"1999-07-23","vote_average":4.493,"backdrop_path":"/7OsGo8yVkTgD1ZJMBi9M8GP5aes.jpg","original_title":"Inspector Gadget","original_language":"en"},{"id":462677,"adult":false,"title":"Doraemon: Nobita's Great Adventure in the Antarctic Kachi Kochi","video":false,"overview":"Doraemon and Nobita discover a mysterious golden ring far beneath the ice in Antarctica, leading them to uncover an ancient, ruined city.","genre_ids":[16,12,14,10751],"popularity":1.7946,"vote_count":101,"poster_path":"/hcydn0Lr3DAixZFOaUmjoqoIFU6.jpg","release_date":"2017-03-04","vote_average":6.485,"backdrop_path":"/3W2I33pTXWMiH8py382Zg86OB9Q.jpg","original_title":"映画ドラえもん のび太の南極カチコチ大冒険","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1057872,"adult":false,"title":"Tokyo Revengers 2 Part 1: Bloody Halloween - Destiny","video":false,"overview":"Hinata is murdered again by the Tokyo Manjikai Gang in front of Takemichi. In order to save Hinata, Takemichi travels 10 years back in time again. Takemichi has to change a key case that can save Hinata. The key case involves a sad incident that occurred to 6 men, who later formed the Tokyo Manjikai Gang.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"popularity":0.9098,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/y0ff6LqAqzD3Ecdy6xPSJJj8TRb.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-21","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/eQsHkIQ4eYwrxazqJyE3oxttRzQ.jpg","original_title":"東京リベンジャーズ2 血のハロウィン編 -運命-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1057873,"adult":false,"title":"Tokyo Revengers 2 Part 2: Bloody Halloween - Final Battle","video":false,"overview":"Driven by a single-minded determination to protect his friends and save Hinata, Takemichi Hanagaki enters a gang war with the hope of altering the course of fate and creating a better future for everyone.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"popularity":1.0904,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/8AegXj6RMEx8WPmJ3YUl4VLsUcu.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-30","vote_average":6.783,"backdrop_path":"/4GeA8aWilTOJ1L2GgiQt6v2A7eq.jpg","original_title":"東京リベンジャーズ2 血のハロウィン編 -決戦-","original_language":"ja"},{"id":402,"adult":false,"title":"Basic Instinct","video":false,"overview":"Catherine, a novelist with an insatiable sexual appetite, becomes a prime suspect when her boyfriend is brutally murdered -- a crime she had described in her latest story.","genre_ids":[53,9648],"popularity":6.4,"vote_count":4272,"poster_path":"/76Ts0yoHk8kV